The evidence with the title 'Sandy Hook elementary school shooting - wikipedia ' says The Sandy Hook Elementary School shooting occurred on december 14, 2012, in Newtown , Connecticut, United States, when 20-year-old Adam Lanza fatally shot 20 children between six and seven years old , as well as six adult staff members . Before driving to the school, he shot and killed his mother at their Newtown  ... . Lanza then drove to Sandy Hook Elementary School in his mother's car . 
